  "texts": [
    "Impact of LLMs evolutionWhile we executed all of our experiments running gpt-3.5 due to its cost-effectiveness and accuracy, one may argue that more advanced LLM models may lead to even better results.",
    "In the following, we show preliminary experiments of zero-shot ADL-LLM using the more advanced gpt-4o model on the MARBLE dataset.",
    "Table 7 shows that gpt-4o improves the F1-score by +4% over gpt-3.5-turbo-0125.",
    "These results indicate that using more advanced LLMs, it is possible to even surpass DeepConvL-STM trained on the whole training set (see Table 2).",
    "However, this performance gain comes with a significant increase in costs, since at the time of writing running experiments with gpt-4o is 10 times more expensive than with gpt-3.5-turbo-0125."
